\s2 Apostles infuriate Sadducees
\p 
\v 29 \w So|strong="G2532"\w* \w in|strong="G2532"\w* answer \w Peter|strong="G4074"\w* \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* Apostles \w said|strong="G3004"\w*: “\w One|strong="G3588"\w* \w must|strong="G1163"\w* \w obey|strong="G3980"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w rather|strong="G3123"\w* \w than|strong="G2228"\w* \w men|strong="G3588"\w*.
