\v 24 \w Well|strong="G2532"\w* \w seeing|strong="G3708"\w* \w one|strong="G5100"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w being|strong="G2532"\w* wronged, \w he|strong="G2532"\w* defended \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w avenged|strong="G1557"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w one|strong="G5100"\w* \w being|strong="G2532"\w* \w oppressed|strong="G2669"\w*, \w striking|strong="G3960"\w* \w down|strong="G3960"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* Egyptian.
