\s1 Jerusalem
\p 
\v 15 \w So|strong="G1161"\w* \w after|strong="G3326"\w* \w those|strong="G3588"\w* \w days|strong="G2250"\w* \w we|strong="G1161"\w* got ready \w and|strong="G1161"\w* \w went|strong="G3778"\w* \w up|strong="G1519"\w* \w to|strong="G1519"\w* \w Jerusalem|strong="G2414"\w*.
